Developer documentation of cosy-pupil-server, external-recorder
===============================================================

External-recorder follows the same guidelines and code conventions as
GtkSourceView:

    https://git.gnome.org/browse/gtksourceview/tree/HACKING

It uses the GLib library (only GLib core, not GObject nor GIO). To have an
overview:

    http://www.gtk.org/
    https://people.gnome.org/~swilmet/gtk-brochure.pdf

You can read an introduction to GLib in the following document:

    https://people.gnome.org/~swilmet/glib-gtk-book/
